&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in Technical Support, Customer Success, Solutions Engineering, Technical Training, or Learning &amp;amp; Development, with a track record of designing and delivering training programs and facilitating workshops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong grasp of modern software development, with hands-on experience in one or more of JavaScript/TypeScript, Node.js, Python, or React, and comfort troubleshooting web apps, APIs, deployments, and cloud-based systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills, with the ability to simplify highly technical concepts for diverse, often non-technical audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep curiosity about AI and emerging technology, ideally with experience around AI products, LLMs, agents, prompt engineering, or AI-assisted development platforms&lt;/li&gt;
